.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-2::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  designer, coach, analyst, freelancer, engineer, project-manager, scientist
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: badminton, cricket, handball, parkour, sailing, snowboarding, soccer
The people use 7 different means of transport: bus, car, roller, scooter, ship, train, trike
 1. the coach is on the right of the person driving the car##1
 2. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is the scientist##1
 6. the designer is the person driving the scooter##1
 7. the designer is between the person who's sport is soccer and the person driving the trike##2
 8. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the engineer##1
 9. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
10. the analyst is on the right of the person driving the ship##1
11. the engineer is on the right of the designer##1
12. the person driving the bus is the coach##1
13. the freelancer is on the left of the designer##1
14. the freelancer is on the right of the person driving the train##1
15. the coach is on the far right##1
16. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the scientist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3       |    4     |   5    |     6     |    7     |
| Job   | project-manager | scientist      | freelancer     | designer  | engineer | analyst | coach |
| Sport         | cricket  | badminton | snowboarding | handball | soccer | parkour   | sailing  |
| Transport     | roller   | train     | trike        | scooter  | ship   | car       | bus      |

