10. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
11. the person who's sport is handball is the owner of the hedgehog##1
12. the person who's sport is handball is the owner of the hedgehog##1
13. the owner of the frog is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
14. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
