.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-16::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  coach, dancer, fisherman, manager, musician, photographer, writer
There are 7 different favourite beverages: sprite, cola, soy-milk, iced-tea, 7up, hot-chocolate, juice
7 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, ferret, guinea-pig, hedgehog, mouse, snake
 1. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the fisherman##1
 2. the owner of the mouse is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking soy-milk##2
 3. the person drinking sprite is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 4. the person drinking juice is on the left of the photographer##1
 5. the person drinking sprite is the coach##1
 6. the fisherman is in the middle##1
 7. the musician is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 8. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
 9. the person drinking sprite is the owner of the chinchilla##1
10. the writer is the owner of the hedgehog##1
11. the coach is on the right of the manager##1
12. the person drinking juice is on the left of the photographer##1
13. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the ferret##1
14. the person drinking cola is on the left of the coach##1
15. the writer is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

